OL,5, Broadcaster Nicky Campbell has claimed 
OL,6, a teacher at two Edinburgh schools     
OL,7, abused children on a "Savile scale".   
OL,9,FHe compared Iain Wares to the disgraced
OL,10,FBBC TV and radio presenter Jimmy Savile
OL,11,Fafter giving evidence to the Scottish  
OL,12,FChild Abuse Inquiry.                   
OL,14,FThe BBC Radio 5Live presenter told the 
OL,15,Finquiry he was sexually and physically 
OL,16,Fabused by other teachers while he was a
OL,17,Fpupil at Edinburgh Academy.            
OL,19,FHe said he witnessed the sexual abuse  
OL,20,Fof a pupil aged about 10 by Mr Wares.  
